{{#if isReact}}
- Prefer function components; colocate small presentational pieces next to features.
- Extract reusable logic into custom hooks (`useThing`) in `src/hooks/` or feature folders.
{{/if}}
{{#if isVue}}
- Prefer `<script setup>` and composables in `src/composables/` or feature folders.
{{/if}}
{{#if isSvelte}}
- Prefer small `.svelte` files; shared logic in `src/lib/` or `src/stores/`.
{{/if}}
{{#if isAngular}}
- Standalone components by default; services for shared logic; keep templates lean.
{{/if}}
{{#if isSolid}}
- Fine-grained reactivity; avoid unnecessary wrappers; colocate route-specific UI.
{{/if}}
{{#if isPreact}}
- Match React patterns where applicable; mind bundle size vs React-only APIs.
{{/if}}
